      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FORREST GUMP (3) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 365m. Great chance to get the job done again. ASTRA BELL (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at Wentworth Park following on from a third place finish (30.17) at this track the start prior. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Key player if finds best. HARD SNIFF STYLE (4) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 17 from 27 starts. Finished in the minors last time when third (30.18) at Richmond making it back to back placings. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Overdue and gets his chance. MAJESTIC PEARL (2) can sneak into the finish again.",
